videoDetails.Title: The Slowest Tank In War Thunder
videoDetails.Description:
Decal link: https://tinyurl.com/42thwzv3

The American T95 Super Heavy Tank, also known as the Doom Turtle, is simultaneously fun and painful to use. On small maps it is an absolute joy thanks to its great armament and armor, but on large maps its low speed absolutely ruins it.

Check the channel "About" section for the link to the creator of my profile picture.
